    <h2 class="text">About</h2>
    <p class="description">I am a Fullstack Developer at <span><a href="http://www.flowstatecreatives.com" target="_blank">Flowstate Creatives</a></span> in Olympia, WA. I have been passionate about computer and software since my childhood. Before getting into developing software, I used to maintain computer software, operating system, and hardware.
  I wanted to know how things work and I decided to study computer science so that I can become a computer scientist.
   I developed an awesome app before graduating 
   from my community college: <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thurstontalk.com/2019/04/23/its-now-easier-than-ever-to-tour-south-puget-sound-community-college/">scavenger hunt </a> app that can guide new and prospective students around the college without the need for a guided tour.
  </p>
